The paper presents a system for answering questions based on the full text of books, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques, which are also relevant to the topic. Finally, the paper mentions the need for commonsense knowledge, which is related to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
